		"description": "<p>With only a thought you can make this fist-sized ball of jagged ice expand to encase your body in a frigid suit of plate armor constructed out of solid black ice.</p>\n<p>As a bonus action, you can reduce the armor to a 5 pound ball of ice which never melts, or expand the ice back into the suit of armor.</p>\n<p>While wearing this plate armor you gain:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>+2 bonus to Armor Class</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>resistance to cold damage</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>once per day you can double your size (as the <em>enlarge/reduce</em> spell) for 10 minutes.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
